HEADWORD: Lobeliaceae
<hw>Lobeliaceae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A natural family of plants not
recognized in all classification systems; in some classifications
lobeliaceous plants are included in family
<fam>Campanulaceae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Lobeliaceae</fam>, lobelia
family.</syn>⟦br⟧
